<pb ed="D" xml:id="D11.8817.0001a" n="0001a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a01"/><milestone unit="juan" n="1"/><cb:mulu type="卷" n="1"></cb:mulu><cb:juan fun="open" n="1"><cb:jhead><g ref="#CB22072">󵘸</g>觀世音三昧經</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a02"/><cb:div><p xml:id="pD11p0001a0201">如是我聞一時佛在毗羅勒<unclear></unclear>栴檀精舎中與諸菩<g ref="#CB16765">󴅽</g>眾
<lb ed="D" n="0001a03"/><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear>人俱二千五百羅漢四部之眾天龍八部皆來雲集<g ref="#CB04694">𠇍</g>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a04"/><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_add_0001a0401" n="0001a0401"/><anchor xml:id="beg0001a0401" n="0001a0401"/>於<anchor xml:id="end0001a0401"/>三昧<unclear></unclear><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_add_0001a0402" n="0001a0402"/><anchor xml:id="beg0001a0402" n="0001a0402"/>无<anchor xml:id="end0001a0402"/>言<g ref="#CB22072">󵘸</g>時諸苐子心生疑惑恠佛所以各
<lb ed="D" n="0001a05"/><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear>世尊嘿然永<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_add_0001a0501" n="0001a0501"/><anchor xml:id="beg0001a0501" n="0001a0501"/>无<anchor xml:id="end0001a0501"/>言<g ref="#CB22072">󵘸</g><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_add_0001a0502" n="0001a0502"/><anchor xml:id="beg0001a0502" n="0001a0502"/>我<anchor xml:id="end0001a0502"/><g ref="#CB21717">󵓕</g><g ref="#CB30130">󷖲</g>眾有何利益
<lb ed="D" n="0001a06"/><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><g ref="#CB30130">󷖲</g>坐而起叉手前白佛言巍巍天尊其意難側
<lb ed="D" n="0001a07"/><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear>請何<g ref="#CB21717">󵓕</g>法問何<g ref="#CB21717">󵓕</g>事思何<g ref="#CB21717">󵓕</g>義受何利益佛今嘿
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D11.8817.0002a" n="0002a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a01"/><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear>無言<g ref="#CB22072">󵘸</g>三界眾生增益邪見便自相向悲涕流淚哀<g ref="#CB21972">󵗔</g>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a02"/>歎曰今日如來入於三昧何時惺悟。</p><p xml:id="pD11p0002a0215" rend="inline">於時世尊即放眉間白
<lb ed="D" n="0002a03"/>豪一光照曜十方遍恒沙界時諸苐子心生歡喜得未曾有
<lb ed="D" n="0002a04"/>各各恭敬立住一面。</p><p xml:id="pD11p0002a0409" rend="inline">尒時佛告諸苐子<g ref="#CB10881">𦗟</g>我所<g ref="#CB22072">󵘸</g>一切大眾
<lb ed="D" n="0002a05"/>各皆合掌聽佛所<g ref="#CB22072">󵘸</g>。</p><p xml:id="pD11p0002a0509" rend="inline">佛言我觀三界空<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_add_0002a0501" n="0002a0501"/><anchor xml:id="beg0002a0501" n="0002a0501"/>无<anchor xml:id="end0002a0501"/>所有亦<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_add_0002a0502" n="0002a0502"/><anchor xml:id="beg0002a0502" n="0002a0502"/>无<anchor xml:id="end0002a0502"/>堅固復
<lb ed="D" n="0002a06"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_add_0002a0601" n="0002a0601"/><anchor xml:id="beg0002a0601" n="0002a0601"/>无<anchor xml:id="end0002a0601"/>有實亦<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_add_0002a0602" n="0002a0602"/><anchor xml:id="beg0002a0602" n="0002a0602"/>无<anchor xml:id="end0002a0602"/>亭息諸法空寂囙緣故有和合則生亦可演<g ref="#CB22072">󵘸</g>亦不
<lb ed="D" n="0002a07"/>可<g ref="#CB22072">󵘸</g>。</p><p xml:id="pD11p0002a0703" rend="inline">尒時觀世音菩<g ref="#CB16765">󴅽</g>白佛言世尊法若可<g ref="#CB22072">󵘸</g>便應不<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_add_0002a0701" n="0002a0701"/><anchor xml:id="beg0002a0701" n="0002a0701"/>无<anchor xml:id="end0002a0701"/>不
<lb ed="D" n="0002a08"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_add_0002a0801" n="0002a0801"/><anchor xml:id="beg0002a0801" n="0002a0801"/>无<anchor xml:id="end0002a0801"/>之法便應可<g ref="#CB22072">󵘸</g>。</p><p xml:id="pD11p0002a0808" rend="inline">佛言善<g ref="#CB21972">󵗔</g>緣合則有緣散則離諸法如是
<lb ed="D" n="0002a09"/><g ref="#CB30130">󷖲</g>緣而生緣<g ref="#CB30274">󷙂</g>則盡。</p><p xml:id="pD11p0002a0909" rend="inline">觀世音菩<g ref="#CB16765">󴅽</g>白佛言如佛所<g ref="#CB22072">󵘸</g>實不<g ref="#CB28933">󷄅</g>也。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a10"/><p xml:id="pD11p0002a1001">尒時阿難白佛言世尊如向所<g ref="#CB22072">󵘸</g>甚難思議亦難側度如佛所
<lb ed="D" n="0002a11"/><g ref="#CB22072">󵘸</g>實將不<g ref="#CB28933">󷄅</g>今便問佛云何名斯經。</p><p xml:id="pD11p0002a1115" rend="inline">佛告阿難此經名觀世
<lb ed="D" n="0002a12"/>音三昧經我於往昔為菩<g ref="#CB16765">󴅽</g>時常見過去佛讀誦斯經吾
<lb ed="D" n="0002a13"/>今成佛亦復讀誦未曾休息我今成佛良由此經此經眀聖難
<lb ed="D" n="0002a14"/>可比度喻如日光能照幽<g ref="#CB07448">𡨋</g>此經亦尒若有比丘比丘<g ref="#CB00112">𡰱</g>優婆塞
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D11.8817.0003a" n="0003a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a01"/>優婆夷受持此經者真我苐子流通正泫法將眀矣三寶不
<lb ed="D" n="0003a02"/><g ref="#CB30274">󷙂</g>興隆正覺盲<g ref="#CB07448">𡨋</g>受悟若有眾生得聞此經念而不忘五刼
<lb ed="D" n="0003a03"/>不堕阿鼻地獄當知此觀世音三昧經正是良藥救人苦難<g ref="#CB31165">󷦽</g>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a04"/>除煩<g ref="#CB08974">𢙉</g>千刼万刼不堕<g ref="#CB08891">𢙣</g>趣當知斯經名大法王法化於人受
<lb ed="D" n="0003a05"/>道百千万億此經難聞亦復難見譬如摩<g ref="#CB00112">𡰱</g>寶珠其眀甚盛
<lb ed="D" n="0003a06"/>照百千界人見歡喜都<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_add_0003a0601" n="0003a0601"/><anchor xml:id="beg0003a0601" n="0003a0601"/>无<anchor xml:id="end0003a0601"/>憂<g ref="#CB08974">𢙉</g>此經亦尒若人得聞必離<g ref="#CB08891">𢙣</g>道。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a07"/><p xml:id="pD11p0003a0701">尒時阿難重白佛言云何行此經復何應現。</p><p xml:id="pD11p0003a0718" rend="inline">佛言阿難若欲
<lb ed="D" n="0003a08"/>行此經應淨房舎中懸諸<g ref="#CB29805">󷑭</g>盖散莘燒香端坐七日念<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_add_0003a0801" n="0003a0801"/><anchor xml:id="beg0003a0801" n="0003a0801"/>无<anchor xml:id="end0003a0801"/>異
<lb ed="D" n="0003a09"/>想誦此觀世音三昧經。</p><p xml:id="pD11p0003a0910" rend="inline">尒時觀世音即自現身其形紫金色
<lb ed="D" n="0003a10"/>身長大二項背日光其色似白銀手捉蓮花現其人前七日之中
<lb ed="D" n="0003a11"/>日有一事初一日時現栴檀勳陸香使行人聞之二日之時於
<lb ed="D" n="0003a12"/>夜半中現大光眀行人得見心大歡喜三日之時現一蓮華大
<lb ed="D" n="0003a13"/>如車輪其華甚盛猶白銀色四日之時現天人身身長一丈
<lb ed="D" n="0003a14"/>身著天衣現彼人前行人見<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_add_0003a1401" n="0003a1401"/><anchor xml:id="beg0003a1401" n="0003a1401"/>已<anchor xml:id="end0003a1401"/>同共娛樂論<g ref="#CB22072">󵘸</g>諸法五日之
<lb ed="D" n="0003a15"/>時即自現身證得三昧自見過去生死刼<g ref="#CB21092">󵉤</g>六日之時復
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D11.8817.0004a" n="0004a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a01"/>現天官五色雜寶所作有四菩<g ref="#CB16765">󴅽</g>端坐<g ref="#CB22072">󵘸</g>法行人見<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_add_0004a0101" n="0004a0101"/><anchor xml:id="beg0004a0101" n="0004a0101"/>已<anchor xml:id="end0004a0101"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a02"/>漸漸心眀眀徹十方即大歡喜奉心敬礼七日之時觀世音
<lb ed="D" n="0004a03"/>菩<g ref="#CB16765">󴅽</g>即自現身其光晃曜眀過於日行人見<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_add_0004a0301" n="0004a0301"/><anchor xml:id="beg0004a0301" n="0004a0301"/>已<anchor xml:id="end0004a0301"/>心甚荒迫
<lb ed="D" n="0004a04"/>觀世音菩<g ref="#CB16765">󴅽</g>即舉左手摩行人頂心得安隱復舉右手指
<lb ed="D" n="0004a05"/>於西方妙樂國土行人尋時即見西方<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_add_0004a0501" n="0004a0501"/><anchor xml:id="beg0004a0501" n="0004a0501"/>无<anchor xml:id="end0004a0501"/>量國國土清淨琉璃
<lb ed="D" n="0004a06"/>寶樹華薗浴池<g ref="#CB08468">𩂜</g><g ref="#CB08468">𩂜</g>皆有行人見<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_add_0004a0601" n="0004a0601"/><anchor xml:id="beg0004a0601" n="0004a0601"/>已<anchor xml:id="end0004a0601"/>煩<g ref="#CB08974">𢙉</g>消除<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_add_0004a0602" n="0004a0602"/><anchor xml:id="beg0004a0602" n="0004a0602"/>无<anchor xml:id="end0004a0602"/>眀根<g ref="#CB31165">󷦽</g>此諸
<lb ed="D" n="0004a07"/>行人<g ref="#CB21717">󵓕</g>世世所生常與觀世音相值復見<g ref="#CB17591">𨶒</g>浮提雜類國土
<lb ed="D" n="0004a08"/>猶如掌中阿摩勒果復見東方阿閦佛國不動如來登王高
<lb ed="D" n="0004a09"/>坐其諸菩<g ref="#CB16765">󴅽</g>多有眷属為人<g ref="#CB22072">󵘸</g>法其地平正名華浴池<g ref="#CB08468">𩂜</g><g ref="#CB08468">𩂜</g>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a10"/>皆有復見北方欝單日國彼土人民壽命長遠永<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_add_0004a1001" n="0004a1001"/><anchor xml:id="beg0004a1001" n="0004a1001"/>无<anchor xml:id="end0004a1001"/>正法可以
<lb ed="D" n="0004a11"/>習誦命終之時當堕<g ref="#CB08891">𢙣</g>道復見上方香積佛國蓮華林茂經
<lb ed="D" n="0004a12"/>行禪室<g ref="#CB01556">𢘻</g>為香華多饒菩<g ref="#CB16765">󴅽</g>復見下方百千万國金剛諸園金
<lb ed="D" n="0004a13"/>剛城金剛坐其諸菩<g ref="#CB16765">󴅽</g><g ref="#CB01556">𢘻</g>在坐上為人<g ref="#CB22072">󵘸</g>法行人見<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_add_0004a1301" n="0004a1301"/><anchor xml:id="beg0004a1301" n="0004a1301"/>已<anchor xml:id="end0004a1301"/>即得六通
<lb ed="D" n="0004a14"/>具八解脫得<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_add_0004a1401" n="0004a1401"/><anchor xml:id="beg0004a1401" n="0004a1401"/>无<anchor xml:id="end0004a1401"/><g ref="#CB01002">㝵</g>智飛到十方随意即至千刼万刼百千億
<lb ed="D" n="0004a15"/>刼度人無量得神通力具陁羅<g ref="#CB00112">𡰱</g>辯才<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_add_0004a1501" n="0004a1501"/><anchor xml:id="beg0004a1501" n="0004a1501"/>无<anchor xml:id="end0004a1501"/>滯樂<g ref="#CB22072">󵘸</g>甚多當
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D11.8817.0005a" n="0005a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a01"/>知此經是大威力七日七夜讀誦此經如前所<g ref="#CB22072">󵘸</g>都<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_add_0005a0101" n="0005a0101"/><anchor xml:id="beg0005a0101" n="0005a0101"/>无<anchor xml:id="end0005a0101"/><g ref="#CB28933">󷄅</g>事若
<lb ed="D" n="0005a02"/>有<g ref="#CB28933">󷄅</g>者我即忘語諸餘經典皆不可信</p><p xml:id="pD11p0005a0216" rend="inline">阿難<g ref="#CB30130">󷖲</g>坐而起合掌讚佛。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a03"/><lg xml:id="lgD11p0005a0301" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em">世尊金剛恵</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">語出皆真實</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">一切諸眾生</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">頗有不信者</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">若不信此經</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a04"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">將堕<g ref="#CB08891">𢙣</g>道中</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">巍巍天中天</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">頗有不歸佛</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">我見魔波旬</l><l rend="text-indent:1em"><g ref="#CB17905">󴗱</g>首來宗仰</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a05"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">今<g ref="#CB22072">󵘸</g>觀世音</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">三昧<g ref="#CB30401">󷛁</g>經典</l></lg><p xml:id="pD11p0005a0511" rend="inline">尒時佛告阿難此經亦名安隱<g ref="#CB08468">𩂜</g>亦名
<lb ed="D" n="0005a06"/>離<g ref="#CB08974">𢙉</g>患亦名除疑惑亦名離<g ref="#CB08891">𢙣</g>道若有比丘犯四重禁五<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_add_0005a0601" n="0005a0601"/><anchor xml:id="beg0005a0601" n="0005a0601"/>无<anchor xml:id="end0005a0601"/>間
<lb ed="D" n="0005a07"/>罪若比丘<g ref="#CB00112">𡰱</g>犯八重禁放恣精神串<g ref="#CB30144">󷗀</g>六情破壞正法若有優
<lb ed="D" n="0005a08"/>婆塞優婆夷犯五<g ref="#CB01618">𨒫</g>罪若有能行此觀世音三昧經<unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a09"/>所<g ref="#CB22072">󵘸</g>眾罪<g ref="#CB01556">𢘻</g><g ref="#CB30274">󷙂</g><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_add_0005a0901" n="0005a0901"/><anchor xml:id="beg0005a0901" n="0005a0901"/>无<anchor xml:id="end0005a0901"/>餘亦見十方淨妙國土如前所<g ref="#CB22072">󵘸</g><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a10"/>異。</p><p xml:id="pD11p0005a1002" rend="inline">佛告阿難若人受持讀誦斯經典者應持此呪難<unclear></unclear><unclear></unclear>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a11"/>亦難值若持此呪應断酒肉不食五辛瞋恚怒<g ref="#CB01556">𢘻</g>為當
<lb ed="D" n="0005a12"/>断諸<g ref="#CB21942">󵖶</g>女色<g ref="#CB01556">𢘻</g>復不為清淨梵行之人乃能受持斯呪。</p></cb:div>
</body>
